01:56.479 --> 01:57.710
the favor to be repaid.

01:58.600 --> 01:59.520
But not right now.

02:10.430 --> 02:11.350
You know what?

02:11.350 --> 02:12.520
It feels like

02:13.800 --> 02:16.520
that time you ran away
from Nanqiao Village,

02:17.840 --> 02:19.840
and we stayed at my grandpa's.

02:20.630 --> 02:22.030
Although it wasn't long ago,

02:23.600 --> 02:24.750
I have a feeling

02:25.990 --> 02:27.670
that it's been ages.

02:30.670 --> 02:31.520
Qiao Qingyu.

02:33.910 --> 02:36.270
I really wanted
to help you leave Huanzhou.

02:46.670 --> 02:47.470
I'm sorry.

02:54.270 --> 02:55.550
You don't need to apologize.

02:57.079 --> 02:58.440
You don't owe anyone anything.

02:59.250 --> 03:02.980
ظآزPerhapsظآز

03:03.480 --> 03:09.150
ظآزThe more we care,
the more careful we becomeظآز

03:10.250 --> 03:15.650
ظآزCounting the distance that separates usظآز

03:16.480 --> 03:22.250
ظآزA single step, and we'd be closer stillظآز

03:27.790 --> 03:31.680
ظآزPerhapsظآز

03:32.250 --> 03:37.800
ظآزWe were afraid of losingظآز

03:38.950 --> 03:44.450
ظآزThat's why we were hesitantظآز

03:45.490 --> 03:48.150
ظآزBut you lingerظآز

03:48.150 --> 03:48.960
Qiao Qingyu,

03:50.150 --> 03:50.870
good night.

03:53.820 --> 03:58.450
