Dance Competition]

05:16.550 --> 05:19.660
[The 7th Youth Starry Cup
Dance Competition]

05:24.180 --> 05:26.420
0823, Qiao Qingyu, are you here?

05:26.420 --> 05:26.990
I'm here.

05:27.270 --> 05:28.950
Qiao Qingyu, you're up next.

05:59.940 --> 06:01.030
I'm sorry, judges.

06:01.030 --> 06:02.500
Something's wrong with her soundtrack.

06:05.180 --> 06:06.710
Why is this happening?

06:06.710 --> 06:07.620
Poor preparation.

09:26.300 --> 09:27.380
Are you leaving?

09:27.380 --> 09:28.380
The results aren't out yet.

09:29.060 --> 09:30.910
All the participants are great dancers,

09:30.910 --> 09:33.030
and I didn't enter for the prizes.

09:33.380 --> 09:34.350
Just being on stage

09:34.500 --> 09:36.110
is enough for me.

09:36.620 --> 09:39.590
You're in touch with yourself.

09:40.260 --> 09:41.550
Thank you for earlier.

09:41.940 --> 09:43.230
A simple thank-you isn't enough.

09:43.790 --> 09:46.260
Qiao Qingyu, it's time
to return my favor.

09:47.150 --> 09:48.380
What do you want me to do?

09:50.740 --> 09:52.260
Once I pass the TEF

09:52.380 --> 09:53.300
and go to France,

09:54.500 --> 09:54.990
I guess

09:54.990 --> 09:56.590
