09:58.310 --> 09:59.500
So I hope you can

09:59.500 --> 10:01.230
leave all your worries behind

10:01.350 --> 10:02.310
today.

10:02.540 --> 10:05.230
Let's have fun today.

10:06.190 --> 10:08.900
Take it as the last memory before I go.

10:35.700 --> 10:41.670
ظآزYou never know. Maybe todayظآز

10:42.190 --> 10:47.520
ظآزThere is a breakthrough coming.
There is a turning pointظآز

10:47.520 --> 10:53.010
ظآز'Cause something changed.
