17:56.590 --> 17:57.350
Qiao Qingyu.

17:57.780 --> 17:58.310
Hmm?

18:00.900 --> 18:01.590
Nothing.

18:01.590 --> 18:03.310
ظآزAnd I realized my helplessnessظآز

18:03.310 --> 18:04.190
This is mine.

18:07.380 --> 18:10.320
ظآزActually, I haven't let goظآز

18:12.810 --> 18:16.780
ظآزIt's just a pretense of silenceظآز

18:19.150 --> 18:22.160
ظآزHow should I find comfortظآز

18:22.540 --> 18:24.230
ظآزIn the unknown years ahead?ظآز

18:25.030 --> 18:30.040
ظآزDon't be so miserable anymoreظآز

18:31.070 --> 18:36.500
ظآزI walked alone
through this heartbreaking streetظآز

18:37.190 --> 18:42.190
ظآزHow can I forget
the sight of you turning back?ظآز

18:43.880 --> 18:46.470
ظآزI gather my courage to forget
the distance between usظآز

18:46.470 --> 18:46.990
How do you like it?

18:47.100 --> 18:48.300
It's breathtaking, isn't it?

18:53.580 --> 18:54.230
Qiao Qingyu.

18:54.230 --> 18:54.780
Hmm?

18:56.390 --> 18:57.260
Close your eyes.

18:57.630 --> 18:58.230
Why?

18:58.470 --> 18:59.540
Just close your eyes.

19:06.430 --> 19:09.190
Don't open your eyes until I say so.

19:10.300 --> 19:11.230
What's it?

19:11.670 --> 19:12.740
Be patient.

19:23.430 --> 19:24.390
Open your eyes.

19:48.500 --> 19:49.670
How did you know?

19:51.710 --> 19:52.990
It doesn't matter.

19:53.390 --> 19:54.230
Make a wish.

20:27.670 --> 20:28.910
What did you wish for?

20:30.230 --> 20:31.390
My first wish

20:31.540 --> 20:33.820
is to get into my dream university.

20:33.910 --> 20:35.020
My second wish

20:35.100 --> 20:37.190
is for my family to stay healthy

20:37.190 --> 20:37.950
and safe.

20:39.500 --> 20:40.340
What about the third one?

20:41.580 --> 20:42.390
It's a secret.

20:42.470 --> 20:43.500
I'm not telling you.

20:45.950 --> 20:47.020
Thank you, Ming Sheng.

20:48.870 --> 20:49.670
You're welcome.

20:54.470 --> 20:56.340
I want to go to Jiangzhou University!

20:59.990 --> 21:00.950
Qiao Qingyu.

21:02.190 --> 21:03.630
I'm so glad we met.

21:06.020 --> 21:07.340
Me too!

21:09.910 --> 21:12.910
All the best to us.

21:13.990 --> 21:15.100
All the best.

21:15.780 --> 21:16.390
Hmm.

21:17.780 --> 21:19.260
Thinking about

21:20.260 --> 21:21.780
relying on myself

21:21.780 --> 21:23.190
to change my life

21:24.990 --> 21:26.780
and decide my own future,

21:28.100 --> 21:30.150
I can't wait to grow up.

21:31.260 --> 21:31.950
Qiao Qingyu.

21:32.230 --> 21:32.670
Hmm?

21:33.540 --> 21:34.340
It's morning.

21:35.670 --> 21:36.630
Time's up.

21:56.390 --> 21:57.710
Ming Sheng.

21:59.390 --> 22:00.710
I wonder

22:01.870 --> 22:03.340
as we grow older

22:04.670 --> 22:07.020
and our lives fill with new experiences

22:07.540 --> 22:09.300
and people,

22:10.060 --> 22:11.340
will

22:13.430 --> 22:15.190
our memories of this time

22:16.910 --> 22:18.670
eventually fade?

22:34.870 --> 22:35.500
Do you remember

22:35.500 --> 22:36.820
the first time we met?

22:39.260 --> 22:40.540
You bit me.

22:42.670 --> 22:43.950
Today, I bit you back.

22:44.430 --> 22:45.870
Now we're even.

22:49.540 --> 22:51.020
From now on, I'll erase

22:53.020 --> 22:54.300
all the memories about you.

22:58.580 --> 22:59.950
I wish you the best of luck.

23:02.060 --> 23:04.390
I hope you get into
your dream university.

24:12.580 --> 24:13.300
Qingyu,

24:13.670 --> 24:15.580
something happened at the noodle house.
Go check it out.

24:15.580 --> 24:16.390
Hurry.

24:17.190 --> 24:18.430
Poor thing.

24:18.870 --> 24:19.540
Look at this.

24:19.540 --> 24:21.150
They're hurting their business.

24:39.340 --> 24:40.670
This is the worst thing
I've ever tasted.

24:42.060 --> 24:44.540
Did you hear that?
That was incredibly rude.

24:44.910 --> 24:46.340
Why are you so rude?

24:46.910 --> 24:48.780
Get out! Throw up outside
if you need to.

24:50.950 --> 24:52.740
Didn't your teacher teach you

24:52.820 --> 24:54.060
about protecting the environment

24:55.670 --> 24:56.820
and hygiene?

24:59.710 --> 25:00.740
Thank you so much.

25:02.630 --> 25:03.230
Sir,

25:03.710 --> 25:05.500
please ignore them.

25:05.670 --> 25:07.430
These brats are thoughtless.

25:08.260 --> 25:09.820
You keep coming back

25:10.190 --> 25:11.950
and affecting our business.

25:12.020 --> 25:13.470
What do you want from us?

25:19.230 --> 25:20.190
My future mother-in-law

25:21.500 --> 25:22.540
and father-in-law,

25:23.500 --> 25:25.060
I might've done something wrong
in the past,

25:25.710 --> 25:27.780
but I'm not small-minded.

25:28.060 --> 25:29.990
I'm here today with good news,

25:30.470 --> 25:31.580
not bad.

25:31.950 --> 25:32.670
Seriously.

25:34.500 --> 25:35.470
Today, I'm here

25:35.740 --> 25:37.820
to confess to Qingyu.

25:37.820 --> 25:38.630
That's what I'm here for.

25:39.190 --> 25:40.670
Don't cause any trouble.

25:42.340 --> 25:43.630
My daughter is young,

25:43.630 --> 25:44.390
and she's not right for you.

25:44.390 --> 25:45.340
So leave now.

25:45.670 --> 25:46.470
Qingyu.

25:46.470 --> 25:47.780
We're meant to be together.

25:47.870 --> 25:48.630
Where are you going?

25:48.630 --> 25:49.340
No.

25:50.260 --> 25:51.870
No.

25:51.870 --> 25:52.870
What are you doing?

25:53.190 --> 25:54.740
Did I tell you to do anything?

25:54.740 --> 25:55.500
Let go!

25:55.870 --> 25:57.390
Did I tell you to do anything?

26:01.670 --> 26:02.470
Qingyu.

26:03.540 --> 26:05.630
I like you, that's why I'm here.

26:05.740 --> 26:07.390
Why would you say I'm making trouble?

26:07.390 --> 26:08.500
Hey. Don't.

26:10.580 --> 26:11.470
Yes?

26:12.870 --> 26:13.580
Nothing.

26:14.870 --> 26:15.670
Qingyu,

26:16.470 --> 26:18.150
age isn't a problem.

26:18.150 --> 26:19.020
Dating me

26:19.950 --> 26:21.430
will make my time in jail worthwhile.

26:21.950 --> 26:23.340
If you reject me,

26:23.510 --> 26:25.390
I'm afraid

26:25.500 --> 26:26.470
I'll be so frustrated

26:26.670 --> 26:28.430
that I might

26:28.430 --> 26:30.020
lose control.

26:30.500 --> 26:30.820
Let go!

26:30.820 --> 26:31.580
We'll call the police!

26:31.580 --> 26:32.300
No!

26:32.950 --> 26:33.870
Are you leaving with me or not?

26:34.540 --> 26:35.870
Let go of him, and I'll go with you!

26:36.340 --> 26:36.870
Come on.

26:38.540 --> 26:39.340
Let's go.

26:39.670 --> 26:41.580
No, you can't do that.

26:41.580 --> 26:42.430
Are you coming or not?

26:42.430 --> 26:42.870
I'll go with you.

26:42.870 --> 26:43.710
Let go of him.

26:44.540 --> 26:45.390
[This is dangerous. Don't imitate.]
Let go of him!

26:46.540 --> 26:47.100
Let go!

26:47.100 --> 26:47.950
Go.

26:48.390 --> 26:49.500
Who are you trying to scare?

26:51.780 --> 26:52.950
Let's all die together!

26:57.300 --> 26:58.820
It's dangerous! Run!

27:00.740 --> 27:01.820
Are you insane?

27:10.780 --> 27:11.580
Mom!

27:11.990 --> 27:13.670
Mom!

27:14.670 --> 27:15.300
Mom!

27:17.430 --> 27:18.580
Mom.

27:50.190 --> 27:50.710
Mom.

27:52.340 --> 27:53.990
What are you doing up here?

27:56.100 --> 27:57.190
Qingyu.

27:59.470 --> 28:00.390
It's nothing.

28:02.990 --> 28:05.390
I think something dropped.

28:07.500 --> 28:08.670
Go back.

28:09.630 --> 28:10.820
I'll stay here for a bit.

28:10.820 --> 28:11.820
I'll be home soon.

28:41.020 --> 28:41.910
Mom.

28:43.020 --> 28:45.740
What's wrong with you, Mom?

28:46.950 --> 28:48.780
Are you feeling alright?

28:49.470 --> 28:51.020
Tell us if something's wrong.

28:51.020 --> 28:52.670
Don't stay out here alone.

28:53.820 --> 28:56.500
Mom.

28:58.470 --> 29:00.870
I noticed the door of the rooftop
was open just now,

29:00.870 --> 29:02.060
and you weren't home.

29:03.540 --> 29:04.470
I don't know...

29:04.580 --> 29:06.950
Say something, Mom.

29:15.990 --> 29:16.710
Qingyu.

29:21.060 --> 29:22.710
How time flies.

29:24.390 --> 29:25.710
You're all grown up.

29:29.020 --> 29:31.580
When you were born,

29:32.870 --> 29:34.390
you were only around two kilograms.

29:35.020 --> 29:37.340
You were like a kitten

29:38.190 --> 29:40.060
with tiny fingers and feet.

29:41.820 --> 29:43.100
I was too scared

29:43.870 --> 29:45.260
to hold you.

29:45.780 --> 29:47.470
I was afraid I might hurt you.

29:49.630 --> 29:50.870
Your sister was different.

29:55.190 --> 29:56.430
When she was born,

29:56.430 --> 29:58.670
her head was round

29:59.580 --> 30:00.740
and perfectly shaped.

30:01.990 --> 30:04.390
Her crying was extremely loud.

30:04.990 --> 30:07.470
Everyone said
she was like a healthy boy.

30:13.990 --> 30:17.300
Both of you are my children,

30:18.500 --> 30:20.540
but you are so different.

30:21.390 --> 30:24.670
Your sister seemed

30:25.710 --> 30:26.990
easy-going

30:27.430 --> 30:28.950
and simple.

30:30.470 --> 30:31.670
But you're different.

30:32.630 --> 30:33.990
Since you were a kid, you've been quiet.

30:36.150 --> 30:37.470
You barely say anything,

30:39.100 --> 30:40.670
but you have a mind of your own.

30:43.300 --> 30:45.540
After we had come to Huanzhou,

30:47.950 --> 30:49.500
many things have happened.

30:50.780 --> 30:51.990
The situation has been more difficult
for you.

30:52.780 --> 30:55.020
Even though you're in a new environment,

30:56.190 --> 30:57.670
your grades haven't dropped.

30:58.300 --> 31:00.670
You've done even better
under great stress.

31:06.500 --> 31:08.500
I see that.

31:11.190 --> 31:12.910
You're a good kid.

31:13.870 --> 31:15.580
But I don't know

31:18.100 --> 31:19.740
why I always want to nag you.

31:20.670 --> 31:23.300
No, Mom. You didn't nag me.

31:24.020 --> 31:24.580
Well...

31:27.060 --> 31:29.230
Every time I see you

31:31.230 --> 31:32.910
acting so carefully in front of me,

31:33.500 --> 31:34.740
my heart breaks.

31:35.950 --> 31:36.630
It's not that.

31:36.630 --> 31:37.670
But I don't know

31:38.100 --> 31:41.670
why I keep going on and on.

31:42.020 --> 31:43.540
I'm scared.

31:43.580 --> 31:44.470
I'm so terrified.

31:47.230 --> 31:48.260
Qingyu,

31:48.910 --> 31:50.820
I'm really scared.

31:51.740 --> 31:53.580
What are you talking about, Mom?

31:56.150 --> 31:56.950
Your sister...

32:03.190 --> 32:04.390
Mom.

32:07.580 --> 32:10.190
She wasn't with me.

32:11.100 --> 32:13.820
She suffered so much.

32:15.230 --> 32:16.300
Even in the end...

32:17.470 --> 32:18.390
In the end,

32:19.300 --> 32:22.820
people wouldn't stop judging her

32:23.100 --> 32:25.670
and kept pointing fingers at her
after her death.

32:25.990 --> 32:28.060
She was young.

32:29.020 --> 32:32.470
Every youngster makes mistakes.

32:32.470 --> 32:36.020
If anyone's to blame,
it's your dad and me.

32:39.710 --> 32:40.990
I regret it.

32:42.190 --> 32:43.390
I regret

32:44.060 --> 32:46.470
that when she came to Shunyun
to find us...

32:47.100 --> 32:49.910
I regret that when she asked

32:50.870 --> 32:52.300
to stay here,

32:52.300 --> 32:54.060
but I wasn't thinking straight

32:54.060 --> 32:57.580
and kept urging her to go back.

33:06.580 --> 33:08.950
I just don't know why.

33:09.710 --> 33:10.500
Am I...

33:10.710 --> 33:12.630
Am I really her mother?

33:13.340 --> 33:15.390
Am I really her mother?

33:15.470 --> 33:18.190
She was asking me for help.

33:23.580 --> 33:25.540
Qingyu.

33:28.060 --> 33:31.950
I caused her death.

33:35.230 --> 33:36.020
Mom.

33:38.190 --> 33:41.430
I don't want
to drag you down, too, Qingyu.

33:41.990 --> 33:45.500
I don't want you
to end up like me and your dad.

33:46.580 --> 33:47.710
I...

33:49.340 --> 33:51.500
Did I hurt you, Qingyu?

33:51.710 --> 33:53.340
I don't want to hurt you.

33:53.340 --> 33:53.910
No, you don't, Mom.

33:53.910 --> 33:55.100
I don't want to hurt you.

33:55.100 --> 33:56.630
Mom, that's not true.

33:57.190 --> 33:58.540
I don't want to hurt you.

33:58.540 --> 34:01.190
I don't want you to end up like us.

34:01.190 --> 34:02.670
I want you to have a better life.

34:02.670 --> 34:04.710
I don't want to hurt you.

34:04.710 --> 34:05.500
Mom.

34:05.630 --> 34:06.870
Did I hurt you, Qingyu?

34:06.870 --> 34:07.870
No, Mom.

34:08.909 --> 34:12.060
Mom, as you said,

34:12.429 --> 34:14.820
Yu and I will go to university,

34:14.820 --> 34:15.989
get jobs,

34:16.020 --> 34:17.949
get married, and have kids.

34:18.340 --> 34:19.870
And we'll always be there for you both,

34:20.949 --> 34:22.230
and make sure you're well cared for.

34:22.230 --> 34:23.989
Why are you saying all this?

34:29.100 --> 34:29.780
Mom.

34:51.989 --> 34:52.739
Doctor,

34:53.150 --> 34:55.429
I'm here to get more sleeping pills
for my mom.

35:00.260 --> 35:01.820
How is she doing lately?

35:02.500 --> 35:03.710
Is she still having trouble sleeping?

35:04.540 --> 35:06.910
She can only sleep
after taking the medicine.

35:08.580 --> 35:10.710
You can adjust the dosage as needed.

35:10.740 --> 35:12.190
But for better effects,

35:12.340 --> 35:14.470
I suggest she comes to see me in person.

35:14.500 --> 35:15.950
I've tried to persuade her many times,

35:15.990 --> 35:17.390
but she refused to come.

35:17.580 --> 35:19.020
Are there any other symptoms?

35:21.870 --> 35:23.430
Her mood is unstable.

35:24.100 --> 35:26.190
She often sits alone, over-thinks,

35:26.190 --> 35:27.630
and cries alone.

35:28.780 --> 35:30.190
When we talk to her,

35:30.430 --> 35:32.270
it's like she doesn't hear us.

35:32.910 --> 35:34.580
She used to be

35:34.580 --> 35:36.100
so full of energy,

35:36.660 --> 35:39.950
but now she seems exhausted.

35:40.950 --> 35:42.100
A few times,

35:42.580 --> 35:44.620
I found her standing
on the rooftop alone,

35:44.620 --> 35:46.270
staring into space.

35:46.310 --> 35:47.140
Have you noticed

35:47.140 --> 35:48.910
any signs of negative emotions

35:48.910 --> 35:50.700
or suicidal thoughts?

35:52.990 --> 35:54.180
Suicidal?

36:07.350 --> 36:08.950
Based on the symptoms you described,

36:08.950 --> 36:10.060
your mom's depression

36:10.060 --> 36:11.750
has likely deteriorated.

36:12.220 --> 36:13.830
I suggest she comes in for treatment
as quickly as possible.

36:13.830 --> 36:15.500
She has to be hospitalized if necessary.

36:15.910 --> 36:17.140
Given her current state,

36:17.140 --> 36:19.790
the risk of suicide is very high.

36:24.020 --> 36:25.990
You need to be more careful

36:25.990 --> 36:27.180
and alert.

36:27.180 --> 36:28.580
Otherwise,

36:28.620 --> 36:31.100
her life would be in danger at any time.

37:06.950 --> 37:07.750
Qingyu.

37:10.060 --> 37:10.870
Hurry.

37:12.430 --> 37:13.220
Ready?

37:23.100 --> 37:24.020
- Good.
- Good.

37:25.180 --> 37:25.620
I'm

37:25.700 --> 37:26.470
grabbing some water.

37:26.500 --> 37:27.950
Come on. Four on four.

37:28.180 --> 37:29.390
Same members, right?

37:30.470 --> 37:31.100
Let's get started.

37:31.100 --> 37:32.390
Come on.

37:34.350 --> 37:36.060
Did you hear about it?

37:36.180 --> 37:37.790
Qiao Qingyu from Class 5

37:37.790 --> 37:39.270
had some trouble at home again.

37:39.540 --> 37:40.790
It's become quite the talk, hasn't it?

37:41.020 --> 37:43.350
The worst part

37:43.500 --> 37:44.950
is that her dad almost set off
a gas tank

37:44.990 --> 37:46.910
at the noodle house yesterday.

38:01.390 --> 38:02.020
Qingyu,

38:02.350 --> 38:03.500
are you satisfied?

38:03.580 --> 38:04.430
I didn't bring any of my sidekicks.

38:04.750 --> 38:05.950
Let's go. I'll buy you bubble tea.

38:06.470 --> 38:08.470
If you don't like that,

38:08.790 --> 38:09.660
let's go have seafood

38:09.990 --> 38:10.790
or hotpot.

38:11.100 --> 38:12.470
Your sister used to like it.

38:13.470 --> 38:14.390
Do you know why your sister

38:14.390 --> 38:15.910
became so famous?

38:16.180 --> 38:17.310
It was all because of me.

38:17.700 --> 38:19.350
I posted the best photos of her

38:19.350 --> 38:20.500
on the Internet,

38:20.500 --> 38:23.870
and that's why she was known
as the prettiest girl in Shunyun.

38:23.950 --> 38:26.100
I made her famous.

38:26.140 --> 38:27.910
I'm the star maker.

38:29.390 --> 38:31.100
But what did she do to me?

38:31.270 --> 38:33.020
She toyed with my feelings.

38:33.390 --> 38:35.540
Luckily, justice was served.

38:35.870 --> 38:37.700
Guess what I found in the hospital.

38:37.910 --> 38:39.870
Your sister had AIDS.

38:46.910 --> 38:48.140
The deeper I loved,

38:49.270 --> 38:50.620
the more I hated her.

38:51.390 --> 38:52.580
So I spread this news

38:52.580 --> 38:54.020
on the Internet.

38:54.140 --> 38:55.910
It went viral right away.

38:56.140 --> 38:57.750
All the comments were talking about her.

38:58.700 --> 39:01.220
The prettiest girl of Shunyun had AIDS.

39:02.390 --> 39:03.830
Many people downloaded her pictures

39:04.500 --> 39:05.580
and wrote comments.

39:06.220 --> 39:07.140
They were all about your sister.

39:07.580 --> 39:09.220
It was crazier than any movie.

39:10.700 --> 39:12.100
Qiao Beiyu had AIDS,

39:12.910 --> 39:14.310
and you're the one who killed her.

39:14.910 --> 39:16.430
I don't want to bother you.

39:16.950 --> 39:18.790
It's you who bugs me, you know?

39:18.870 --> 39:20.220
Do you know how long it took me

39:20.220 --> 39:21.270
to forget this?

39:21.270 --> 39:22.310
If you hadn't posted it on the Internet,

39:22.310 --> 39:23.500
would Qiao Beiyu have killed herself?

39:23.750 --> 39:25.060
What does that have to do with me?

39:25.540 --> 39:26.910
What does that have to do with me?

39:29.390 --> 39:30.470
Did you post it?

39:31.310 --> 39:32.430
Did you?

39:32.500 --> 39:33.620
If you hadn't done that,
would she have killed herself?

39:33.660 --> 39:34.350
You bullied her!

39:34.350 --> 39:35.540
How are you going to compensate her?

39:35.750 --> 39:37.180
Don't you feel sorry for my family?

39:37.180 --> 39:38.430
You're the murderer!

39:38.750 --> 39:39.870
Hei.

39:39.870 --> 39:40.660
It was all because of you!

39:40.660 --> 39:41.220
Hei.

39:41.220 --> 39:42.100
Calm down, Hei.

39:42.180 --> 39:43.060
Enough.

39:43.060 --> 39:43.540
What's going on?

39:48.470 --> 39:49.270
Are you all right?

39:50.790 --> 39:52.220
He's the one
who caused Qiao Beiyu's death.

39:52.950 --> 39:53.790
What?

39:54.580 --> 39:55.700
He's responsible for that.

40:01.180 --> 40:03.180
Hei, I have something to tell you.

40:04.350 --> 40:05.180
She's dead.

40:05.750 --> 40:07.060
They say she jumped into the sea.

40:08.060 --> 40:09.990
Are you insane?
Who are you talking about?

40:10.020 --> 40:11.020
Qiao Beiyu.

40:11.020 --> 40:11.830
Who?

40:11.830 --> 40:12.750
Qiao Beiyu.

40:43.350 --> 40:44.500
To think that

40:44.950 --> 40:46.830
Hei is the cause of her sister's death.

40:47.790 --> 40:50.350
He killed Qiao Beiyu,
yet he's still targeting her sister.

40:51.540 --> 40:53.620
Plus, the NCEE is around the corner.

40:57.870 --> 40:58.870
Sheng,

40:58.870 --> 40:59.870
don't over-think.

40:59.910 --> 41:01.540
You have nothing to do with Qiao Qingyu.

41:01.580 --> 41:03.310
Whatever happens to her
doesn't concern you.

41:03.750 --> 41:04.430
Exactly.

41:09.220 --> 41:09.830
Sheng,

41:10.310 --> 41:12.390
aren't you going to Beining
for the exam?

41:12.660 --> 41:13.180
That's right.

41:13.180 --> 41:14.430
Is everything prepared?

41:14.910 --> 41:15.750
What time is your flight?

41:17.500 --> 41:18.750
Get me

41:19.270 --> 41:20.750
two pairs of sneakers,

41:20.750 --> 41:21.470
okay?

41:23.470 --> 41:24.580
Let's have a toast.

41:24.580 --> 41:26.430
Let's ace these exams.

41:27.140 --> 41:27.910
Stay true in wealth and honor.

41:27.910 --> 41:28.540
Cheers.

42:28.480 --> 42:32.170
ظآزPerhapsظآز

42:32.680 --> 42:38.380
ظآزThe more we care,
the more careful we becomeظآز

42:39.520 --> 42:44.920
ظآزCounting the distance
that separates usظآز

42:45.920 --> 42:51.480
ظآزA single step,
and we'd be closer stillظآز

42:57.150 --> 43:00.820
ظآزIn the futureظآز

43:01.280 --> 43:07.000
ظآزTime will reveal this secretظآز

43:08.500 --> 43:13.570
ظآزWaiting is a silent promiseظآز

43:14.820 --> 43:19.980
ظآزThat never expiresظآز

43:23.580 --> 43:28.050
ظآزTurns out that what's on my mindظآز

43:29.050 --> 43:32.720
ظآزIs your nameظآز

43:33.220 --> 43:38.320
ظآزThe only stubbornness in my heartظآز

43:39.400 --> 43:42.620
ظآزAt first sightظآز

43:43.050 --> 43:46.330
ظآزThe future has been determinedظآز

43:47.020 --> 43:52.580
ظآزDreams began to feel realظآز

43:53.680 --> 43:57.220
ظآزTurns out that what's on your mindظآز

43:57.680 --> 44:01.620
ظآزIs a placeظآز

44:01.920 --> 44:07.480
ظآزWhere the same story is held dearظآز

44:08.150 --> 44:11.520
ظآزFortunately, I'm not sensible enoughظآز

44:11.850 --> 44:15.320
ظآزCourage wasn't late tooظآز

44:15.850 --> 44:21.920
ظآزOnly then does time not betray
our acquaintanceظآز
